- [ ] 3. Create "'`skills/docker-agent/scripts/docker-agent.sh` with shared-lib sourcing, env knobs, helper structure, and CLI parser.
- [ ] 4. Implement Dockerfile discovery that supports both repo-wide recursion and `CHANGED_FILES` filtering, with clear skip behavior.
